            <cato:entity-ref entity-type="uscode" value="usc/33/1314/a/9">33 U.S.C. 1314(a)(9)</cato:entity-ref>
          </external-xref>)</cato:entity> is amended by adding at the end
			 the following:</text>
			<quoted-block display-inline="no-display-inline" id="HC8E9F2A8EE0641D7BB339E5CF6D90C19" style="OLC">
				<subparagraph id="H70772E2F18C741B1875E5C7629C09EFC">
          <enum>(C)</enum>
          <header>Publication of
				Pathogen and Pathogen Indicator List</header>
          <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">Upon publication of the new or revised
